* This addon are based on the projekt dokuwiki
- dokuwiki-2006-11-06 (http://www.splitbrain.org/projects/dokuwiki)

* Requirements:
- PHProjekt version 5.2 (http://www.phprojekt.com/)

* Aim:
- This addon add a the Dokuwiki to PHProject.

* Installation: see file INSTALL

* Features:
- Dokuwiki with the default plugins and template

* Todo:
- using groups from PHProjekt.

* Tips:
a) To use the addon on PHProjekt installation who are not in the Docroot, you must change some files (see INSTALL). 
b) The dokuwiki plugins, how are not distributed with dokuwiki,  are not tested yet. Try them on your own risk.
c) The dokuwiki use UTF-8 Codepages but the PHProjekt don't use UTF-8. While you are in the dokuwiki addon the special char in the PHProjekt naviagtion bar are not readable.


* FAQ:

Q: It is posible to make the dokuwiki only readable to one group?
A: Yes it is posible but you must edit this hardcode in the doku.php on the addon directory. See the INSTALL.

Q: Can i restrict some parts of the dokuwiki to PHProjekt groups?
A: No, this is at the moment not posible.
